{"tid":2151394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有興趣一齊了解下唔同嘅文化議題？","createTime":"2020-08-11T11:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T17:02:18.000Z","uid":169802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"16ae2a82d3cbffa3a4b0742f569061f9e42aefe1","tid":2151394,"uid":169802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:04:49.000Z","msg":"事源我有三個00後心境嘅80後麻甩佬朋友好鐘意鳩噏想搵個平台同大家吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想幫佢地將呢件咁正嘅事分享畀大家～<br />\n<br />\n佢哋會一路打機一路同大家講唔同嘅議題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兒時回憶、宗教、文化、組織嗰啲乜鳩都講<br />\n之但係佢地最大嘅特色就係講嘅內容或者人物同組織會盡量唔提，目的就係等大家「靠估」(當然唔係真係想大家估估下啦)，其實希望可以引起大家本身嘅興趣，有興趣嘅自然會自己搵架啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家逢星期二晚(通常9-11pm左右)，無論OT緊定準備瞓覺，入去同佢地一齊吹水互相交流，同埋幫手狠批佢地打機廢之餘又成日挑起我條求知欲！搞到我Netflix條playlist 成個疫情期間都未必睇得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經有大量片等住大家：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgmtDcIT_JZzMn4hUUZNtXA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCgmtDcIT_JZzMn4hUUZNtXA&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9Fvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=890f89f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgmtDcIT_JZzMn4hUUZNtXA</a>"},{"pid":"098302501b67bced79e680430f8a779e9deccf8b","tid":2151394,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:05:56.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"ee09623fc1ad347492a405972cfbf63bee9aaf9c","tid":2151394,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:07:30.000Z","msg":"正正經經聽蕭生d學者學下野啦"},{"pid":"17b58d57b3683be3e22130e48d2b78c3ef01652d","tid":2151394,"uid":162574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:40:35.000Z","msg":"聽過講黑社會個集，都幾得意"},{"pid":"139e6170eb336bb65